ຍິນດີ! ນີ້ແມ່ນຕົວຢ່າງ endpoint PUT ໃນ FastAPI ເພື່ອອັບເດດຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້ສະເພາະໂດຍ ID:

```python
from fastapi import FastAPI, HTTPException
from pydantic import BaseModel

app = FastAPI()

class UserUpdate(BaseModel):
    name: str | None = None
    email: str | None = None

users_db = {
    "1": {"name": "ສົມບັດ", "email": "sombat@example.com"},
    "2": {"name": "ດາວັນ", "email": "davan@example.com"}
}

@app.put("/users/{user_id}")
async def update_user(user_id: str, user: UserUpdate):
    if user_id not in users_db:
        raise HTTPException(status_code=404, detail="User not found")

    current_user = users_db[user_id]
    update_data = user.model_dump(exclude_unset=True)
    for key, value in update_data.items():
        current_user[key] = value

    users_db[user_id] = current_user
    return {"message": "User updated successfully", "user": current_user}
```
ສົ່ງ request PUT ໄປທີ່ `/users/{user_id}` ພ້ອມ body JSON ທີ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈະອັບເດດ. ລອງເບິ່ງເດີ້!

