**โค้ดที่กระชับขึ้นด้วย Map Literal:**
```go
package main

import "fmt"

func createMap() map[string]int {
	return map[string]int{
		"apple":  3,
		"banana": 5,
		"orange": 2,
	}
}

func main() {
	fmt.Println(createMap())
}
```
